   (:div :class "section"
         (:h1 "Tabs Suck.")
         (:p "As a paradigm, tabs work for well for inexperienced users, they
provide a simple visual representation that's easy to follow.
Unfortunately that's where the benefits end. Users often spend
several frustrating minutes combing through tabs to find what they are
looking for. To get beyond this point, and do some real work, you need
something more powerful.")
         (:figure
          (:img :src "/static/img/tab_overflow.png")
